      <title>周末消息称英国和毛里求斯就查戈斯群岛前期付款达成一致</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/uk-mauritius-agree-on-front-load-pay-for-chagos-week-end-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《周末报》周日报道称，英国已同意毛里求斯提出的要求，即预先支付每年 9000 万英镑（1.1 亿美元）的租赁补偿金，作为查戈斯群岛交易的甜头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/uk-mauritius-agree-on-front-load-pay-for-chagos-week-end-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 09:28:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚国家元首称最新袭击事件标志着仇恨犯罪上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/australia-state-head-says-latest-attacks-mark-rise-in-hate-crime</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新南威尔士州州长克里斯·明斯周日表示，最近针对犹太教堂和犹太人财产的袭击标志着澳大利亚反犹太仇恨犯罪的升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/australia-state-head-says-latest-attacks-mark-rise-in-hate-crime</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 04:34:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚反对党竞选活动聚焦生活成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/australia-opposition-focuses-on-living-costs-in-campaign-launch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚主要反对党在为 5 月 17 日举行的下届选举开展竞选活动时，将生活成本和住房问题列为优先事项。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/australia-opposition-focuses-on-living-costs-in-campaign-launch</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 04:05:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国将新日铁终止美国钢铁竞标的最后期限延长至 6 月</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/us-extends-deadline-for-nippon-steel-to-end-us-steel-bid-to-june</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据美国钢铁公司发表的声明称，美国外国投资委员会批准延长新日本制铁公司放弃以 141 亿美元收购美国钢铁公司的最后期限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/us-extends-deadline-for-nippon-steel-to-end-us-steel-bid-to-june</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 03:56:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>立法者称与特朗普讨论 SALT 扣除上限“积极”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/salt-deduction-cap-talks-with-trump-positive-lawmakers-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约州、加利福尼亚州和新泽西州的众议院共和党人对州和地方税收减免上限感到不满，他们认为周六晚间与唐纳德·特朗普就该问题进行的会谈是“积极的”，但表示候任总统并未做出任何坚定承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/salt-deduction-cap-talks-with-trump-positive-lawmakers-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 02:16:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>万斯称不应赦免 1 月 6 日的暴力抗议者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/vance-says-violent-jan-6-protesters-shouldn-t-be-pardoned</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选副总统 JD Vance 缓和了其老板赦免所有参与 2021 年 1 月 6 日美国国会大厦骚乱的抗议者的承诺，称那些行为暴力的人“显然”不应该得到赦免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/vance-says-violent-jan-6-protesters-shouldn-t-be-pardoned</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 01:33:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾称中国“怪物”船重返争议海域</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/philippines-says-china-s-monster-ship-back-in-disputed-waters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾称，一艘被广泛称为“怪物”的中国海警巨型船已返回其南海专属经济区，这促使其海警船接近并发出无线电挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/philippines-says-china-s-monster-ship-back-in-disputed-waters</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 01:05:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>如果确认领导财政部，Bessent 将出售对冲基金股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/bessent-to-sell-hedge-fund-stake-if-confirmed-to-lead-treasury</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普挑选的美国财政部部长斯科特·贝森特（Scott Bessent）如果得到参议院的批准，将辞去 Key Square Group 的职务并出售其在合伙企业中的股份，以避免利益冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/bessent-to-sell-hedge-fund-stake-if-confirmed-to-lead-treasury</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 11 Jan 2025 21:58:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普调查结束，特别检察官杰克·史密斯辞去司法部职务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/special-counsel-jack-smith-resigns-from-doj-as-trump-probes-end</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据政府周六提交的法庭文件显示，杰克·史密斯已辞去负责监督当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的联邦刑事调查的特别顾问职务，并已“脱离”美国司法部。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/special-counsel-jack-smith-resigns-from-doj-as-trump-probes-end</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 11 Jan 2025 21:29:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>洛杉矶大火向东北蔓延，威胁贝莱尔和布伦特伍德</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/weather-set-to-heighten-los-angeles-fire-risks-after-respite</link>
      <description><![CDATA[毁灭性的帕利塞兹大火向东北方向推进，在短暂的喘息之后，更多干燥风的威胁加剧了风险，迫使南加州极其富裕的布伦特伍德和贝莱尔社区重新进行疏散。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/weather-set-to-heighten-los-angeles-fire-risks-after-respite</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 11 Jan 2025 12:13:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
